The Zoning Resolution of the City of New York, effective as of December 15, 1961, and as subsequently amended, is further amended by changing the Zoning Map, Section No. 18a, by changing an R2 district to a R3-2 R3-1 district bounded by a line 100 feet northerly of Avenue O, East 26th Street, Avenue O, and a line midway between East 26th  Street and Bedford Avenue, as shown on a diagram (for illustrative purposes only) dated August 26, 2019 and subject to the conditions of CEQR Declaration E-541, Borough of Brooklyn, Community District 14.

Adopted.

